        "start": 123.28,
        "end": 145.68
      },
      {
        "segment": "Had it chosen to follow its will at any space time during its teachings, several times as you call this measure.",
        "start_offset": 1837,
        "end_offset": 2277,
        "start": 146.96,
        "end": 182.16
      },
      {
        "segment": "This entity had the possibility of moving towards the martyr's place which was for that martyr Jarusala.",
        "start_offset": 2304,
        "end_offset": 2659,
        "start": 184.32,
        "end": 212.72
      },
      {
        "segment": "Yet in meditation this entity stated time and egging.",
        "start_offset": 2702,
        "end_offset": 2877,
        "start": 216.16,
        "end": 230.16
      },
      {
        "segment": "So that all mind, a body, a spirit complexes shall addie to the third density illusion.",
        "start_offset": 4646,
        "end_offset": 4936,
        "start": 371.68,
        "end": 394.88
      },
      {
        "segment": "That is that each yellow ray, a physical, a complex, a body, shall cease to be reliable.",
        "start_offset": 4966,
        "end_offset": 5195,
        "start": 397.28000000000003,
        "end": 415.6
      },
      {
        "segment": "It is a misnomer to for this reason alone, call each mind, body, spirit, complex a martyr.",
